    "body" : "You haven&#39;t shown the the screenshot of the dialog that is being opened, when you select &quot;File&quot; -&gt; &quot;New&quot; -&gt; &quot;Other...&quot;. Instead you have shown the menu item itself from the menu. Also, there is a &quot;Project...&quot; menu item you can use."
