    "comment_id" : 140467615,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "What is shown in the <i>File &gt; New</i> menu directly (and not only in <i>File &gt; New &gt; Other...</i>) depends on the actual perspective (which can be chosen in <i>Window &gt; Perspective</i>). According to your screenshot, your actual perspective is <i>Java EE</i>. It seems you have switched from the <i>Eclipse IDE for Enterprise Java and Web Developers</i> to the <i>Eclipse IDE for Java Developers</i> which does not support the <i>Java EE</i> perspective. Click the button in the upper right corner to switch to the <i>Java</i> perspective or choose a different supported perspective via <i>Window &gt; Perspective</i>."
  }, {
